<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.iwanami.co.jp/jpworld/text/ClosedCountry01.html" class="external text" title="http://www.iwanami.co.jp/jpworld/text/ClosedCountry01.html" rel="nofollow">Questioning Japan's 'Closed Country' Policy on Refugees</a></li>
