<li id="cite_note-125"><b><a href="#cite_ref-125" title="">^</a></b> Policy of the <a href="/wiki/Party_for_the_Netherlands" title="Party for the Netherlands">Party for the Netherlands</a> of <a href="/wiki/Hilbrand_Nawijn" title="Hilbrand Nawijn">Hilbrand Nawijn</a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20070312113228/http://www.hilbrand-nawijn.nl/c_news.asp?nummer=557" class="external text" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20070312113228/http://www.hilbrand-nawijn.nl/c_news.asp?nummer=557" rel="nofollow">"De 25 kernpunten uit het programma van Partij voor Nederland"</a>. Archived from <a href="http://www.hilbrand-nawijn.nl/c_news.asp?nummer=557" class="external text" title="http://www.hilbrand-nawijn.nl/c_news.asp?nummer=557" rel="nofollow">the original</a> on 2007-03-12<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20070312113228/http://www.hilbrand-nawijn.nl/c_news.asp?nummer=557" class="external free" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20070312113228/http://www.hilbrand-nawijn.nl/c_news.asp?nummer=557" rel="nofollow">http://web.archive.org/web/20070312113228/http://www.hilbrand-nawijn.nl/c_news.asp?nummer=557</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=De+25+kernpunten+uit+het+programma+van+Partij+voor+Nederland&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20070312113228%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.hilbrand-nawijn.nl%2Fc_news.asp%3Fnummer%3D557&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Multiculturalism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-126"><b><a href="#cite_ref-126" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://pub.tv2.no/nettavisen/english/article254421.ece" class="external text" title="http://pub.tv2.no/nettavisen/english/article254421.ece" rel="nofollow">Right-wing politicians want to ban Islam</a>. Ban Islam manifesto at <i><a href="http://precaution.ch/wp/?page_id=3" class="external text" title="http://precaution.ch/wp/?page_id=3" rel="nofollow">Le devoir de précaution</a></i></li>
