<li id="cite_note-128"><b><a href="#cite_ref-128" title="">^</a></b> Foreign Policy Centre.<a href="http://fpc.org.uk/fsblob/792.pdf" class="external text" title="http://fpc.org.uk/fsblob/792.pdf" rel="nofollow">Born in the UK: Young Muslims in Britain</a><sup class="noprint Inline-Template"><span title="&#160;since November 2008" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Dead_external_links" title="Wikipedia:Dead external links">dead link</a></i>]</span></sup>'.</li>
